\n中西區（西區、中環、金鐘、半山、山頂）<br />\n灣仔、銅鑼灣、天后、炮台山: 維園中央草坪<br />\n鰂魚涌、太古、西灣河、筲箕灣: 沿海旁<br />\n小西灣、杏花邨、柴灣: 柴灣公園<br />\n鑽石山、黃大仙: 黃大仙廣場<br />\n九龍灣、牛頭角、觀塘: 觀塘海濱公園<br />\n大圍、沙田、馬鞍山 : 沙田百步梯<br />\n元朗、天水圍: 天水園公園<br />\n屯門: 屯門公園<br />\n南區: 鴨利洲風之塔公園<br />\n<br />\n仲有獅子山同山頂人鏈!"},{"pid":"0389c793058b235b00f2e17afeaffb25cbe9001f","tid":1565730,"uid":317299,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-13T09:41:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/XySvw4Z.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FXySvw4Z.jpg&h=8251e762&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/hqGL5pZ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FhqGL5pZ.jpg&h=af6e3036&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"d1bddebf150f6680f8da6a2526a614410d4e3dba","tid":1565730,"uid":49042,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-13T09:52:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"76805c99cdb98d5125912d017426b1daff09d56b","tid":1565730,"uid":49042,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-13T10:25:21.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"c0262247479120f1f462bbec90fa1f1467f3c38f","tid":1565730,"uid":49042,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-13T10:51:56.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"99715c66dfb06b43b82a17167df580d66026c75d","tid":1565730,"uid":49042,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-13T11:03:59.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"ee672eab66027375c92fe5dd73dbbdf38d2b8a5e","tid":1565730,"uid":49042,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-13T11:31:30.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"983173adcf36dcb077702b72815c5a0734c8c45a","tid":1565730,"uid":49042,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ff1b6711870912b070c1e82a4d0f8a83c0bd8e58","tid":1565730,"uid":49042,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-13T09:12:21.000Z","msg":"(CD-ROM 借表姐account)<br />\n<br />\n我係2020年DSE考生<br />\n開左t